          tellus at, auctor suscipit metus. Duis congue nibh at tortor ornare, sed commo do ipsum mattis.</p>

        <br>

        <div class="widget widget-contact no-margin-bottom">

          <ul>
            <li>
              <i class="fa fa-map-marker"></i>
              4124 Peachtree Street, Atlanta, <br class="visible-lg-block"> GA 30301
            </li>
            <li>
              <i class="fa fa-phone"></i>
              770-613-0234
            </li>
            <li>
              <i class="fa fa-envelope"></i>
              <a href="mailto:coliman@bellsouth.net">coliman@bellsouth.net</a>
            </li>
          </ul>

        </div><!-- widget-contact -->

        <br><br>

        <div class="social-media">

          <a class="pinterest" href="#"><i class="fa fa-pinterest"></i></a>
          <a class="linkedin" href="#"><i class="fa fa-linkedin"></i></a>
          <a class="instagram" href="#"><i class="fa fa-instagram"></i></a>
          <a class="facebook" href="#"><i class="fa fa-facebook"></i></a>
          <a class="twitter" href="#"><i class="fa fa-twitter"></i></a>

        </div><!-- social-media -->

      </div><!-- col -->
    </div><!-- row -->
  </div><!-- container -->

  <br class="hidden-lg hidden-md"><br class="hidden-lg hidden-md">

  <div class="map no-margin-bottom" data-zoom="15" data-height="565" data-address="6404 Pleasantdale Rd, Doraville, GA, USA">
